Since I have been such a vocal opponent of Steve in this debate over his
proposal to repeal Summary Adoption, I would like to take the opportunity to
say I was, and am now, in agreement with Steve that SA was an extremely
dangerous mechanism and one which needed immediate action to correct.  So
while I honestly feel that Steve's attempt should be judged as having
failed, I applaud him for his efforts, if not his means, against this great
evil.

Of course I am in favor of similar, but safer, mechanisms.

-Macross


